<div class="howto_section">
  <h2>Setting Up New Study</h2>

  <p>Please provide us with the following information so that we may process your request to create a new study: </p>

  <ul>
    <li>Name of the study</li>
    <li>Name of the data streams that will be used to collect data in the study (i.e., PAM, Mobility, and ohmage)</li>
    <li>Information on the survey that will be used in the study for self-report</li>
    <ul>
      <li>Name of the survey (e.g., Post Surgical Pain-Witkin)</li>
      <li>Version (Version 2, March 2015)</li>
      <li>The name and email address of the researcher</li>
      <li>Device type: iphone, android or both</li>
      <li>Target study start date and duration</li>
      <li>Target number of participants</li>
      <li>Description (2 sentences)</li>
      <li>The survey questions</li>
    </ul>
  </ul>

  <p>Please send the information above to xxxxxx@gmail.com. We will inform you when the study is ready for testing by you and your staff and after feedback when it is ready for participants.</p>


